text_ar": "صَيْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, TA,) likewise said of an arrow, (S, M, TA,) signifies the same; (S, TA;) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SAb", "text_ar": "صاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "said of an arrow is intrans. (M.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "alone, [as though used elliptically,] (Msb, TA,) inf. n. as above; (Msb, K;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SAb", "text_ar": "صاب", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaSuwbu", "text_ar": "يَصُوبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, Msb,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SayobuwbapN", "text_ar": "صَيْبُوبَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SawobN", "text_ar": "صَوْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Msb, K;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SAb", "text_ar": "صاب", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaSiybu", "text_ar": "يَصِيبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SayobN", "text_ar": "صَيْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Msb;) likewise said of an arrow, (S, Msb,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It went right; did not deviate from the right course:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, * TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it reached"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "hit"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the object of aim."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naHowa Alr~imiy~api", "text_ar": "نَحْوَ الرِّمِيَّةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SAb", "text_ar": "صاب", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M, A, TA,) aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaSuwbu", "text_ar": "يَصُوبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A, TA,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SawobN", "text_ar": "صَوْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SayobuwbapN", "text_ar": "صَيْبُوبَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M, TA,) said of an arrow, (M, A, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It went right towards the thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "animal, shot at;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, TA;) as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb AlqiroTaAsa", "text_ar": "اصاب القِرْطَاسَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, TA,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb fiY AlqiroTaAsi", "text_ar": "اصاب فِى القِرْطَاسِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) [said of a man, as is indicated by the context in the S and TA,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He hit the butt,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "target;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he did not miss the butt,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "target."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "alone is said of an archer or the like [as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He hit the object of his aim"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (Msb:) one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ramaY faA^aSaAba", "text_ar": "رَمَى فَاَصَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He shot,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cast, and hit the object of his aim"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) ―         -b3-  [Hence, likening an event, &c., to an arrow,] one says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu A^amorN", "text_ar": "اصابهُ اَمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An event smote him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "befell him;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SAbhu", "text_ar": "صابهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaSuwbuhu", "text_ar": "يَصُوبُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SawobN", "text_ar": "صَوْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", signifies the same. (Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aSaAbatohu muSiybapN", "text_ar": "اَصَابَتْهُ مُصِيبَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An affliction,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a calamity,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "smote him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "befell him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu Al$~aYo'u", "text_ar": "اصابهُ الشَّىْءُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The thing reached him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "so as to take effect upon him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (Mgh, * Msb:) whence the saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aSaAbahu", "text_ar": "اَصَابَهُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino qawoli Aln~aAsi maA A^aSaAbahu", "text_ar": "مِنْ قَوْلِ النَّاسِ مَا اَصَابَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "There reached him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the sayings of the people, what reached him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]. (Msb.) [Thus tropically used,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu", "text_ar": "اصابهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "may generally be rendered"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It hit, struck, smote, wounded, hurt, affected, assailed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "befell, him."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "One says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu maraDN", "text_ar": "اصابهُ مَرَضٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wajaEN", "text_ar": "وَجَعٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbthu riyHN", "text_ar": "اصابتهُ رِيحٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", &c., (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A disease,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pain,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "smote, affected,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "assailed, him."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlmaTaru", "text_ar": "المَطَرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaAbahu", "text_ar": "صَابَهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, Msb,) aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaSuwbuhu", "text_ar": "يَصُوبُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SawobN", "text_ar": "صَوْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Msb,) (assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The rain fell,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "lighted, upon him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it; wetted him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, was rained upon."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~amaA='u AlA^aroDa", "text_ar": "السَّمَا=ءُ الاَرْضَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaAbati", "text_ar": "صَابَتِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e. (assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sky,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "clouds,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "rain,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "watered the earth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "land, copiously:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Lth, M, TA:) or it means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aSaAbatohaA biSawobK", "text_ar": "اَصَابَتْهَا بِصَوْبٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it smote it with rain;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sent rain upon it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (M, L, TA.) In the following verse, cited by IAar,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "fakayofa turaj~iY AlEA*ilaAtu tajal~udiY\n                      \n                     \n                        HamiymuhaA ↓ \n      waSaboriY A_i*aA maA Aln~afosu Siyba"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "he explains"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Siyba", "text_ar": "صِيبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as being like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "quSida", "text_ar": "قُصِدَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and says that it may be of the dial. of him who says"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaAba Als~ahomu", "text_ar": "صَابَ السَّهْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; but [ISd remarks,] I know not how this is, for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaAba Als~ahomu", "text_ar": "صَابَ السَّهْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is not trans.; [though, as shown above, he has mentioned it as being trans.;] and in my opinion, [he says,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Syb", "text_ar": "صيب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "here is from the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaAbati Als~amaA='u AlA^aroDa", "text_ar": "صَابَتِ السَّمَا=ءُ الاَرْضَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[expl. above; the meaning of the verse being,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "But how should the censuring women hope for my constraining myself to behave with hardiness, and for my being patient, when the beloved of the soul has been smitten"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by death, or by the decree of death; for ISd adds,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kaA^an~a Almaniy~apa SaAbati AlHamiyma faA^aSaAbatohu", "text_ar": "كَاَنَّ المَنِيَّةَ صَابَتِ الحَمِيمَ فَاَصَابَتْهُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biSawobihaA", "text_ar": "بِصَوْبِهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (M, TA. *) ―         -b4-  ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is also used in many phrases in which its agent is likened to an archer.] One says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb AlS~awaAba", "text_ar": "اصاب الصَّوَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He hit the right thing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "point,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the object,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "aim, of his words"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of his actions"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (A:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb Als~adaAda", "text_ar": "اصاب السَّدَادَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[which means the same]. (S in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sd", "text_ar": "سد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "alone [means thus likewise; or] (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he said,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "did, that which was right."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K. *) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb fiY qawolihi wafiEolihi", "text_ar": "اصاب فِى قَوْلِهِ وَفِعْلِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He hit the right thing in his saying and his deed;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb;) and so"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY raA^oyihi", "text_ar": "فِى رَاْيِهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in his opinion; contr. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^axoTaA^a", "text_ar": "اَخْطَاَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb bigoyatahu", "text_ar": "اصاب بِغْيَتَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He attained,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "obtained, the thing that he sought,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wanted:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "whence the saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb mino zawojatihi", "text_ar": "اصاب مِنْ زَوْجَتِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[and so app."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aSaAbahaA", "text_ar": "اَصَابَهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "safaqa", "text_ar": "سَفَقَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ")] (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He obtained his desired enjoyment of his wife:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb min~iY", "text_ar": "اصاب مِنِّى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "occurs in a trad., [as a euphemism,] said by the wife of Handhaleh, meaning (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He compressed me:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh:) and it is said in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kaAna yuSiybu mino raA^osi baEoDi nisaAy^ihi", "text_ar": "كَانَ يُصِيبُ مِنْ رَاْسِ بَعْضِ نِسَايِهِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wahuwa SaAy^imN", "text_ar": "وَهُوَ صَايِمٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He used to kiss"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the head of some one or more of his wives when he was fasting"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA: and the like is said in the Mgh.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb mina AlmaAli wagayorihi", "text_ar": "اصاب مِنَ المَالِ وَغَيْرِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He took,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "took with his hand, of the property and other things."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb Al$~aYo'a", "text_ar": "اصاب الشَّىْءَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He hit upon,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "lighted on, the thing;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he found the thing."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, K, * TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu", "text_ar": "اصابهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He found it, met with it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "experienced it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "namely, a good or an evil event. And (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He found it out,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "discovered it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "namely, an enigma (see 8 in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hjw", "text_ar": "حجو"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") or the like. And] (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He found it to be right:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he saw it, considered it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "held it, to be right."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA. [See also 10.]) And (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He aimed at it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(As, TA;) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he desired, wished, willed, intended,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "meant, it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(As, M, A, Msb, TA.) One says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aSaAba fulaAnN", "text_ar": "اَصَابَ فُلَانٌ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlS~awaAba faA^axoTaA^a AljawaAba", "text_ar": "الصَّوَابَ فَاَخْطَاَ الجَوَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one aimed at, and desired,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[to say]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that which was right,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(As, Msb, * TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and failed of giving rightly the reply."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(As, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ayona tuSiybaAni", "text_ar": "اَيْنَ تُصِيبَانِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Whither do ye two desire to go?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; a saying of Ru-beh. (TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tajoriY biA^amorihi ruxaA='F Hayovu A^aSaAba", "text_ar": "تَجْرِى بِاَمْرِهِ رُخَا=ءً حَيْثُ اَصَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the Kur [xxxviii. 35, referring to the wind], has been expl. as meaning (assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Running by his command softly,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gently,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "whithersoever He desireth."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, * TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb A@ll~`hu Al~a*iY A^araAda", "text_ar": "اصاب ا@للّٰهُ الَّذِى اَرَادَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", said in a trad., in reply to a question respecting the interpretation of a text, means (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "God desireth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "meaneth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[thereby,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what He desireth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "meaneth."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb A@ll~`hu bika xayorFA", "text_ar": "اصاب ا@للّٰهُ بِكَ خَيْرًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^araAdahu", "text_ar": "اَرَادَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  [i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "May God intend thee good"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "alone (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He desired,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "intended,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "meant, that which was right."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K. *) One says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu bixayorK", "text_ar": "اصابهُ بِخَيْرٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  [meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He did good to him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (El-Muärrij, TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Asw", "text_ar": "اسو"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) [But]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu bika*aA", "text_ar": "اصابهُ بِكَذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iSaAbapN", "text_ar": "اـِصَابَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) with which are syn. ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muSaAbN", "text_ar": "مُصَابٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[in"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 1741}, {"kind": "text", "text": "accordance with a usage generally allowable] (S, TA) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muSaAbapN", "text_ar": "مُصَابَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K, TA,) (assumed tropical:)  [generally] means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He afflicted him with,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by, such a thing;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gave pain to him thereby."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K: * in the latter, only the inf. n. of the verb in this sense; and so in other senses.) [Thus one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu bi$ar~K", "text_ar": "اصابهُ بِشَرٍّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He afflicted him with evil;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "did evil to him:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu bimakoruwhK", "text_ar": "اصابهُ بِمَكْرُوهٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He afflicted him with,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "did to him, an abominable,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an evil, thing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "action:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu biqawolK qabiyHK", "text_ar": "اصابهُ بِقَوْلٍ قَبِيحٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He afflicted him with,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "said to him, a foul saying:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu bi*aHolK", "text_ar": "اصابهُ بِذَحْلٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He punished him by blood-revenge:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAbhu", "text_ar": "اصابهُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bimaraDK", "text_ar": "بِمَرَضٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(i. e. God,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a thing,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "affected him with disease;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "rendered him diseased:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and in many similar cases, the phrase may be well rendered with a verb derived from the noun; like phrases in which “ affecit ” (a Latin equivalent of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") occurs; as in “ honore affecit, ” meaning “ honoravit. ”] El-Hárith Ibn-Khuld El-Makhzoomee says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "rajulFA↓A^aZulayomu A_in~a muSaAbakumo\n                      \n                     \n                        A^ahodaY Als~alaAma taHiy~apF Zulomu"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "O Dhuleymeh, verily your afflicting a man who has given the salutation of peace, greeting, is tyranny"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: IB says that this verse is not of El- 'Arjee, as El-Hareeree imagined it to be: the correct reading is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aZulayomu", "text_ar": "اَظُلَيْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as above:"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zlym", "text_ar": "ظليم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is an apocopated from of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zulayomapu", "text_ar": "ظُلَيْمَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; which is the dim. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zaluwm", "text_ar": "ظَلُوم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": some read"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aZaluwmu", "text_ar": "اَظَلُومُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and some,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asulayomu", "text_ar": "اَسُلَيْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": [the verse is cited accord. to this last reading in the S:]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rajulFA", "text_ar": "رَجُلًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is governed in the accus. case by"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muSaAb", "text_ar": "مُصَاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as an inf. n.]: and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zulomu", "text_ar": "ظُلْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is the enunciative of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~a", "text_ar": "اـِنَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (L, TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aSaAbahumu Ald~ahoru binufuwsihimo waA^amowaAlihimo", "text_ar": "اَصَابَهُمُ الدَّهْرُ بِنُفُوسِهِمْ وَاَمْوَالِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Time,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fate, afflicted them by destruction,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "extirpation, among themselves and their cattle,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "possessions."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M.) [In the K,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA_iSaAbpu", "text_ar": "الاـِصَابةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is expl. as signifying"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlAiHotiyaAju", "text_ar": "الاِحْتِيَاجُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": but the right reading is evidently"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlAijotiyaAHu", "text_ar": "الاِجْتِيَاحُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as Ibr D has remarked in the margin of my copy of the TA; so that"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASAb", "text_ar": "اصاب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He destroyed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "extirpated;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "agreeably with an explanation in the sentence next preceding above, from the M.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mano yuridi A@ll~`hu bihi xayorFA yuSibo minohu", "text_ar": "مَنْ يُرِدِ ا@للّٰهُ بِهِ خَيْرًا يُصِبْ مِنْهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (assumed tropical:)  occurring in a trad., means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Him whom God intendeth good He trieth with afflictions,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "that He may recompense him for them. (TA.) And one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA kunotu muSaAbFA walaqado A^uSibotu", "text_ar": "مَا كُنْتُ مُصَابًا وَلَقَدْ اُصِبْتُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  [app. meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I was not affected with weakness of intellect,"}, 